Populate Region, Country and other Dictionary tables with data for normalization and completeness in ODS: 11

 

Double click on the PackageOds-SRandST.dtsx. If it’s the first time, you will be presented with a blank pane on the Control Flow Task. 

·         Drag and drop 1 Execute SQL Task from SSIS Toolbox on to the Control Flow Task and name it appropriately as shown in the screenshot below.  Double Click the Execute SQL Task to complete populating Region data in ODS.

 





 

·         Drag and drop 1 Data Flow Task from SSIS Toolbox on to the Control Flow Task and name it appropriately as shown in the screenshot below.  Successively, drag and drop 6 Execute SQL Tasks on to the Control Flow Task rename them appropriately as shown.  Link these objects with Precedence Constraints as shown.  This is to load the Staff-to-Patient Ratio Dataset into ODS.
